{"tid":1646034,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（經濟戰）日日黃絲日/全城最黃獎賞","createTime":"2019-10-11T06:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T06:42:48.000Z","uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c0321e66cc63ab4fb3094dc0b040d7f97f90c9c","tid":1646034,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"在我喝某家黑衣減幾蚊奶茶的時候，我想了一個辦法凝聚黃絲並且支持黃絲經濟。<br />\n我發現<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">淨係有黃藍地圖是不夠的，很多人過兩天就忘記</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我建議<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要用優惠建立黃絲商圈</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黃絲商舖提供優惠給黃絲</span></strong>，順道<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏無原則的廢中廢老</span></strong><br />\n方法有以下這些：<br />\n1.穿<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">指定服裝</span></strong>享受優惠，例如黑衣（奶茶店模式）<br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">急口令</span></strong>，例如30秒內唱完榮光可享受優惠（麥當當模式）<br />\n<br />\n3.展示<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">某特定物品</span></strong>享優惠，例如手機上的連登App或者 hkmap.live，可享優惠<br />\n贊成請正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />並幫推到黃絲老闆睇到並留言給意見<br />\n反對請負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家補充"},{"pid":"e8f7db6c18037d3f9fcdf9dcda556c76d14a3307","tid":1646034,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:42:48.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}